            Your consent is timestamped and stored securely for legal compliance and audit purposes.<br><br>

            16. EFFECTIVE DATE<br><br>
            This Privacy Policy is effective as of December 17, 2025  and was last updated on December 17, 2025.<br>
            This document supersedes all previous versions of the RGDC Dental Management System Privacy Policy. The terms of this Privacy Policy will govern your use of the system from the effective date forward.<br><br>

